Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.78,en,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that means "clean." These are dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.12,en,,0000,0000,0000,,The idea is to resolve the tension.
