Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.51,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like an arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.22,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:10.01,en,,0000,0000,0000,,But, see, then the other aspect is stability,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:11.93,en,,0000,0000,0000,,a company that you can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.48,en,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you can balance those ideas
