Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.70,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Benjamin! Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:36.29,en,,0000,0000,0000,,They switched babies on me at the hospital, didn't they, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.75,en,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how'd you do in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.46,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I got the judge to postpone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.84,en,,0000,0000,0000,,the alimony hearing for another 21 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.09,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:47.17,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've got till Monday to find out which S and L and which municipality
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.84,en,,0000,0000,0000,,my son-in-law stashed all that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:50.18,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.89,en,,0000,0000,0000,,But, anyway, I thank you and my daughter thanks you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:53.18,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're welcome, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.14,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.69,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye, Junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:13.70,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's very creative, Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.37,en,,0000,0000,0000,,He liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:24.71,en,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, he actually liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.01,en,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go in. Your father's making
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:38.27,en,,0000,0000,0000,,a television appearance for his campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.85,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Dad, I've got to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.06,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:44.98,en,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to go on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.98,en,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.41,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.75,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's move our seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:13.18,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then I quit as your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:18.10,en,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you believe that annoying loser guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.10,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you should have just punched him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.27,en,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Just punched him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.35,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.44,0:07:23.60,en,,0000,0000,0000,,- What do you mean? - You boxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:25.40,en,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've shoved him around,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:26.73,en,,0000,0000,0000,,- shut him up. - Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.03,en,,0000,0000,0000,,- I could take you. - Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.57,en,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who I could take.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.28,en,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've even kicked him in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:32.53,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Kicked him in the face?
