Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:38.20,en,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, real cute, Leigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.87,en,,0000,0000,0000,,- Let's sit outside. - How much do I owe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.16,en,,0000,0000,0000,,It's taken care of.
